# Workflow and Project Structure

- **Planning Before Coding:**
  - Define the flow in detailed pseudocode step-by-step before coding.
  - Confirm your logic and structure before writing actual code.
  
- **Project Structure:**
  - Technologies: Next.js, React, TypeScript, CSS Modules, and GSAP.
  - Suggested structure:
    ```
    app/
      ├── layout.tsx
      └── page.tsx

    components/
      ├── common/
      ├── sections/
      └── layout/

    constants/
      ├── about.ts
      └── skills.ts

    hooks/
      └── useExample.ts

    styles/
      └── app.scss
    ```
  - For each component, create a folder with:
    ```
    name-component/
      ├── index.tsx
      └── class.modules.scss
      └── use-[name-component].ts
    ```

